#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Activate the QML/JS debugger with a specified port. The value must be of "
"format port:1234[,block], where block is optional and will make the "
"application wait until a debugger connects to it."
msgstr ""

